definition: valuable/precious/to value/to treasure/to set store by

sentences.english: A valuable road map for understanding and healing cybersex addictions.
sentences.chinese: 一个网络性爱的理解和治疗吸毒成瘾宝贵的路线图。

sentences.english: The Dunnings have a wealth of stories from the time they spent with Jackson.
sentences.chinese: 邓宁斯有一段与杰克逊共同度过的宝贵的人生经历。

sentences.english: Tea is one of the greatest cultural treasures of Chinese civilization.
sentences.chinese: 茶是中华文明最宝贵的文化财富之一。

sentences.english: This is the most precious treasure of which Dragon & Lion takes the utmost pride.
sentences.chinese: 这是龙狮最为自豪和值得骄傲的宝贵财富。

sentences.english: The nectar plants are precious wealth to mankind.
sentences.chinese: 蜜源植物资源是人类的宝贵财富。

sentences.english: This has provided valucapable data to stay in soil improvement.
sentences.chinese: 这为土壤改良任务给予了宝贵信息。

sentences.english: All this took up much of my precious time.
sentences.chinese: 这些事情占用了自己很多宝贵的时间。

sentences.english: They know the life is so costful , and an unromantic living with the true happiness.
sentences.chinese: 知道生命有多么宝贵，而一份平淡的生活就是幸福。

sentences.english: How precious to me are your thoughts, O God!
sentences.chinese: 神阿，你的意念向我何等宝贵。

sentences.english: They can also be invaluable in creating a well versed cadre of NCOs and Officers.
sentences.chinese: 这样打造出精通熟练的士官和军官干部是非常宝贵的。

sentences.english: Meanwhile, Li Dazhao said that today is most precious.
sentences.chinese: 同时，李大钊说过，当下是最宝贵的。

sentences.english: I resent all these encroachments on my valuable time.
sentences.chinese: 我“不满”所有这些占用了我的宝贵时间的行为。

sentences.english: This has provided valuable data for extension of cultivable land.
sentences.chinese: 这样就提供了有关扩大可耕地面积的宝贵数据。

sentences.english: The nectar and pollen plants are precious wealth to mankind.
sentences.chinese: 蜜粉源资源是人类的宝贵财富。

sentences.english: And above were costly stones, after the measures of hewed stones, and cedars.
sentences.chinese: 上面有香柏木和按着尺寸凿成宝贵的石头。

sentences.english: Faith is your greatest asset to overcome the barriers that keep you from moving forward.
sentences.chinese: 信心是你最宝贵的资产，克服难阻你前进的障碍。

definition: to place great importance on/to treasure
to be deficient in sth/to be short of sth (supplies, money etc)
